## 7. Train State Machine

```
    +-----------------------------------------------+
    |                                               |
    v                                               |
+-------+     +------------+     +------------+     |
|  FIT  |---->| IN-SERVICE |---->| AVAILABLE  |----+
+---+---+     +------------+     +-----+------+
    |                                  |
    |         +------------+           |
    +-------->|   UNFIT    |<----------+
              +-----+------+
                    |
                    v
              +------------+
              |MAINTENANCE |
              +-----+------+
                    |
                    v
              +------------+
              |    FIT     |
              +------------+
```

| State | Definition | Transitions |
|-------|------------|-------------|
| **FIT** | Train operationally ready | IN-SERVICE, UNFIT |
| **IN-SERVICE** | Running revenue service | AVAILABLE |
| **AVAILABLE** | Fit but not assigned | IN-SERVICE, UNFIT |
| **UNFIT** | Requires maintenance | MAINTENANCE |
| **MAINTENANCE** | Undergoing maintenance | FIT |

---

